![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1d24d1d3-b0b6-4719-8dc4-b53be6e4372c/e243.jpg?format=original)

Spider-Man turns 60 this year and the party has not stopped as we celebrate all things Spidey. This week, we tackle one of the best modern stories in recent history....Spider-Verse! Not only is the tale a love letter to all things Spider-Man but it produced some of the best Spider-Man variants ever! We discuss the comic, the animated movie, and other multiversal Spidey adventures in this super fun episode of the Major Issues Podcast!  
  
Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [**ComicBookClique.com**](episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

  
